      • getShade

        int getShade()
        specifies a darker version of its input color. A 10% shade is 10% of the input color combined with 90% black. Be aware that OOXML also returns values greater than 100%.(指定其输入颜色的较暗版本。10%色调是指输入颜色的10%加上90%黑色。请注意，OOML还返回大于100%的值。)
        Returns:
        the value of the shade specified as percents in the range [0..100000] (usually ...) with 0% indicating minimal shade and 100% indicating maximum or -1 if the value is not set(指定为范围[0.]内的百分比的色调值100000]（通常……）0%表示最小色调，100%表示最大色调，如果未设置值，则为-1)

      • getTint

        int getTint()
        specifies a lighter version of its input color. A 10% tint is 10% of the input color combined with 90% white. Be aware that OOXML also returns values greater than 100%(指定其输入颜色的较亮版本。10%色调是指输入颜色的10%与90%白色相结合。请注意，OOXML也返回大于100%的值)
        Returns:
        the value of the tint specified as percents in the range [0..100000] (usually ...) with 0% indicating minimal tint and 100% indicating maximum or -1 if the value is not set(指定为范围[0.]内的分量的色调值100000]（通常……）0%表示最小色调，100%表示最大色调，如果未设置值，则为-1)
